      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty. I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and the interior is still looking totally fresh. I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will love it just as much as I have. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
