    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The chassis remains taut with documented subframe reinforcement and refreshed bushings. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox offers crisp engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior shows zero signs of oxidation or paint correction needs. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the VANOS system has been overhauled, and valve clearances are within factory spec. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
